        "summary": "Delete bill of quantities.",
        "description": "This endpoint enables the deletion of multiple bills of quantities at once by providing an array of ids. If the\noperation is successful, you will receive a response containing the deleted items list. Keep the API's rate limit\nin mind when making requests. If possible, use the option to delete multiple records at once to save resources\nand time.",
        "operationId": "Projects|Bill of quantities_deleteAction",
        "parameters": [
