        ],
        "summary": "Fetch vehicle list.",
        "description": "This endpoint enables you to retrieve a directory of vehicles within geoCapture, each of which is fitted with a\nGPS tracker. The `driverName` in the vehicle is only configured if a driver is specified in the vehicle settings.\nIt will not provide you with the current driver from stamps.",
